ournals \n📋 Trackers \n📆 Calendars \n📌 Notepads \n📱 Templates \n📖 Digital notebooks \n✏️ Study guides \n📑 Checklists\n...and almost ANY other printable or digital product you can dream up!\n\nThat's exactly why I created my course \"Create in Canva: How To Create Printable Planners\" - to teach you these fundamental skills through step-by-step videos AND a detailed workbook!\n\n❤️❤️ Comment CICPLANNERS so you can start creating digital products today!\n\nNo more staring at blank Canva pages wondering where to start. Let's turn those ideas into profitable products! \n\nNow here's those instructions I promised you:\n✨ Create an announcement or secret reveal\n✨ Cover it up with any elements you choose\n✨ Duplicate the page & move the elements off the 2nd page leaving just a little bit showing\n✨ Make sure Grid view and Duration are on \n✨ Hover your mouse between the pages - Add transition - Select Match & Move\n✨ Increase the time \n✨ Adjust the length of each page, if needed\n✨ Hit Play & reveal the big news!\n\nFollow for more Canva tips and digital product tutorials @imjenmichele\n\n🔥 Share with a friend who NEEDS to know how to do this! \n\n#digitalproductsforbeginners #digitalproductstosell #howtostartanonlinebusiness #howtousecanva #howtocreatedigitalproducts #howtoselldigitalproducts #howtosellonetsy #digitalshop #etsydigitalsellers #workingmomsolutions #canvapro #canvassador #createdigitalproducts #canvalovers #canvadesign\".","note":"","type":"image","user":{"$ref":"users","$id":6938240},"cover":"https://scontent-ber1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/553315490_17953952558991771_1848732944554600786_n.jpg?stp=cmp1_dst-jpg_e35_s640x640_tt6&_nc_cat=104&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0xJUFMuYmVzdF9pbWFnZV91cmxnZW4uQzMifQ%3D%3D&_nc_ohc=4pTOOyAKTfsQ7kNvwFIiL4i&_nc_oc=AdrTYxnPiAPj5wcshSr1Z3TN5a1khgdQBJHFncqC64wpbzdNumCN4zMxDYNgbwRWvGk&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-ber1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_gid=P2TkNDW2Zq32xvetA3EhoA&_nc_ss=7a289&oh=00_Af20c365BtfIWj4QilDu